&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8 - 10 years experience in selling software solutions, working with US financial institutions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven knowledge about&amp;nbsp; AVS, account validation, fraud prevention, or payment risk solutions, as well as understanding of US payment rails (ACH/Nacha, RTP, FedNow)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commercial acumen with the ability to drive sales processes from lead generation to successful deal close&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to engage C-level executives, navigate complex organizations, and orchestrate executive alignment during the sales process.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Entrepreneurial Spirit: You are comfortable with ambiguity and &quot;unknowns.&quot; You don&#39;t need a finished manual to start selling; you help build the manual.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive Communicator: You don&#39;t wait for instructions. You reach out to colleagues in the NL, ask for what you need, and anticipate market shifts before they happen.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consultative Pitcher: You can translate complex technical features into clear business ROI for executive stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary + variable remuneration&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;17 paid holidays&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pension: We offer a 401(k)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health insurance&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;MacBook Pro, iPhone, and all the tech you need&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A culture of ownership, innovation, and autonomy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quarterly company meetup in The Netherlands&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A diverse team of 35+ nationalities, driven by impact&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
