&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About SurePay&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Founded in 2016, SurePay is the leading account verification platform, relied upon by 250+ banks and thousands of organizations, to prevent fraud, misdirected payments, and reputational damage. Headquartered in Utrecht, we are scaling our platform and our team across Europe and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’ve spent the last two years actively shaping EU legislation to ensure our Account Verification Services (AVS) became the gold standard. After successfully lobbying for a safer financial landscape, we’ve emerged as the&amp;nbsp; EU market leader in Account Verification (VOP, CoP), widely considered the standard in the industry. We have outgrown the &quot;blank canvas&quot; startup phase, but we are not a rigid corporate machine. We currently service about 225 banks in 16 countries. We have been building and expanding our product suite and are looking for a new colleague. We have been building and expanding our product suite and are looking for a new colleague.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a VP Business Development you will own the entire commercial domain with the goal of growth across Europe—spanning Sales, Presales, and Partnerships. Your objective is to leverage our commercial teams and focus on Tier-1 banks as our primary channel to reach their corporate clients.&amp;nbsp; Focus will be on adding new logos as well as complex, strategic cross-selling (e.g., Fraud Risk Indicators and Global Solutions) of our additional products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead a multidisciplinary team to reclaim &quot;home markets&quot; where local schemes currently dominate and penetrate top European banks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategy Execution: Own and implement the &quot;Bank-as-a-Channel&quot; model across the EU and UK. You will orchestrate Sales, Account Directors, Inside Sales, and Partnerships to ensure our services are sold to and through major financial institutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Team Leadership &amp;amp; Evolution: Lead and mentor a team of ~12 direct reports located primarily in NL, with local presence in DE, UK, and BE.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will evaluate the current structure and evolve it to support complex, high-value technical sales.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tier-1 Pursuit: Personally drive or provide &quot;heavy-weight&quot; support for engagements with enterprise bank targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cross-Functional Synergy: Act as the bridge between the market and our Product/Marketing teams. You must translate complex technical solutions into clear commercial value propositions, navigating local markets and regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
